[21.086122, "o", "                                       \u001b[1;4mWhat Does APME Catch?\u001b[0m                                        \r\n\r\n\u001b[1mL\u001b[0m вҖ” Lint: FQCN, modes, task names, free-form, bare vars \u001b[1mM\u001b[0m вҖ” Modernize: deprecated loops, bare       \r\nincludes, Python 2 \u001b[1mR\u001b[0m вҖ” Risk: shell injection, privilege escalation, insecure downloads \u001b[1mSEC\u001b[0m вҖ”        \r\nSecrets: passwords, API keys, tokens (Gitleaks) \u001b[1mP\u001b[0m вҖ” Policy: module allow/deny, argument validation  \r\n"]
